{"lemma":"ضَنَى","slug":"ضَنَى","root":"ض.ن.#","root_slug":"ض-ن-_","root_link":"/words/roots/ض-ن-_","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n26088","n26093","n26095"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B6%D9%8E%D9%86%D9%8E%D9%89"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n26088","headword_ar":"ضَنِىَ","root":"DnY","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DanFY","text_ar":"ضَنًى"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, M, Mgh, Msb, K;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ADTnY","text_ar":"اضطنى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same;"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, slender, and small in body:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and hence, (Ham p. 112,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, diseased, disordered,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sick;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, and Ham ibid.;) because disease occasions leanness, or emaciation: (Ham:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, lean,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"emaciated:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(so accord. to the explanation of the inf. n. in the Mgh:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, affected with a disease, disorder,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sickness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of long continuance, and settled,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"constant, so that he was at the point of death,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as infected,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pervaded, him, and so that, whenever he thought himself to be recovering, he relapsed."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)       -A2-  [See also 1 in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dnw","text_ar":"ضنو"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["S","M","Msb","K","Ham"]},{"entry_id":"n26093","headword_ar":"ضَنًى","root":"DnY","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": inf. n. of 1. (S, M, &c.) ―         -b2-  Also, [in some copies of the K erroneously written"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaniY~N","text_ar":"ضَنِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DanK","text_ar":"ضَنٍ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, M, Msb, K;) the former applied alike to a man (Fr, IAar, T, S, Msb) and to a woman (IAar, T, S, Msb) and to two persons (Msb) and to a pl. number, (Fr, IAar, T, S, Msb,) because originally an inf. n., (S, Msb,) for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*uw DanFY","text_ar":"ذُو ضَنًى"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*aAtu DanFY","text_ar":"ذَاتُ ضَنًى"},{"kind":"text","text":"[&c.]; (Msb;) or some do not dualize it nor pluralize it, because it is [originally] an inf. n., and others dualize it and pluralize it; (M;) but ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DanK","text_ar":"ضَنٍ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"has a fem. (Msb) and a dual and a pl., (S,) its fem. being"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaniyapN","text_ar":"ضَنِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, TA) [and its dual"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaniyaAni","text_ar":"ضَنِيَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aDonaA='N","text_ar":"اَضْنَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Slender, and small in body:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and hence, (see 1,)]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"diseased, disordered,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sick:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) [or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lean,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"emaciated:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see again 1:)] or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affected with a disease, disorder,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sickness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of long continuance, and settled,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"constant, so that he is at the point of death,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as infects,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pervades, him, and so that, whenever he thinks himself to be recovering, he relapses."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tarakotuhu DanFY","text_ar":"تَرَكْتُهُ ضَنًى"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaniyFA","text_ar":"ضَنِيًا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I left him lean,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"diseased,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]. (S.)"}],"source_refs":["Fr","IAar","T","S","Msb","TA","M","K"]},{"entry_id":"n26095","headword_ar":"ضِنًى","root":"DnY","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", [written in the TA"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DnA","text_ar":"ضنا"},{"kind":"text","text":", but the final radical is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":",] with kesr, accord to IAar, signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Pains that cause fear."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]}}